+** The following functions can be used to advance and query a changeset 
+** iterator created by this function:
+**
+** <ul>
+**   <li> [sqlite3changeset_next()]
+**   <li> [sqlite3changeset_op()]
+**   <li> [sqlite3changeset_new()]
+**   <li> [sqlite3changeset_old()]
